            "mimeType": "text/html",
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE HTML><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Download YouTube Videos as MP3 or MP4 files for free with Y2Mate, your favorite YouTube to MP3 converter. No sign-up or software required.\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><title>Y2Mate - Free YouTube to MP3 Converter</title><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://v3.y2mate.nu/\"><style>body{background-color:#fafafa;background-image:linear-gradient(#121212 168px, transparent 168px);background-repeat:no-repeat;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;margin:0;}input, button{font-family:inherit;}.header{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}.header a{color:#b4b4b4;text-decoration:none;margin-right:16px;}.header a:last-child{margin-right:0;}form{background-color:#ffffff;max-width:600px;border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0px 12px 32px -8px rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.12), 0px 4px 12px -4px rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.06);margin:32px auto 0 auto;padding:32px 24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;box-sizing:border-box;}form button, form input{height:48px;border-radius:6px;}.form__title{color:#363636;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;line-height:16px;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;}.form__input input{color:#595959;background-color:#fafafa;font-size:16px;width:100%;border:1px solid #e2e2e2;padding:0 12px;outline:none;box-sizing:border-box;}.form__actions{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;}.form__formats{background-color:#fafafa;border:1px solid #e2e2e2;height:48px;border-radius:6px;padding:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;box-sizing:border-box;} .form__formats button[type=\"button\"]{color:#494949;background-color:transparent;font-size:14px;border:none;height:34px;padding:0 24px;cursor:pointer;}.form__formats button[type=\"button\"].active{color:#ffffff;background-color:#121212;}.form__actions button[type=\"submit\"]{color:#ffffff;background-color:#d62828;font-size:16px;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:0 24px;}.form__input--progress{color:#595959;background-color:#fafafa;width:100%;height:48px;border:1px solid #e2e2e2;border-radius:6px;padding:0 12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;justify-content:left;box-sizing:border-box;}.form__loader{width:16px;height:16px;border:2px solid #e2e2e2;border-top-color:#d62828;border-radius:50%;animation:spin 0.8s linear infinite;}@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}.form__actions--download{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;}.form__actions--download button.another{color:#363636;background-color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;border:1px solid #e2e2e2;padding:0 12px;cursor:pointer;}.form__actions--download button.another:disabled{color:#b4b4b4;background-color:#fafafa;cursor:not-allowed;}.form__actions--download button.download{color:#ffffff;background-color:#d62828;font-size:16px;border:none;padding:0 24px;cursor:pointer;}.form__actions--download button.download:disabled{cursor:not-allowed;opacity:0.4;}.form__error--title{color:#363636;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;line-height:16px;}.form__error--message{color:#595959;background-color:#fafafa;font-size:16px;line-height:48px;height:48px;border:1px solid #e2e2e2;border-radius:6px;padding:0 12px;box-sizing:border-box;}.form__error--button{display:flex;justify-content:right;}.form__error--button button{color:#ffffff;background-color:#d62828;font-size:16px;border:none;padding:0 12px;cursor:pointer;}.text{color:#494949;max-width:600px;margin:48px auto 0 auto;}.text h1{color:#363636;font-size:22px;line-height:22px;margin:0;}.text p{font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:16px 0 0 0;}.text ol{list-style-position:inside;margin:16px 0;padding-left:0;}.text li{line-height:24px;margin-bottom:8px;}.text li:last-of-type{margin-bottom:0;}.text a{color:#363636;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;}.footer{text-align:center;max-width:600px;border-top:1px solid #e2e2e2;margin:64px auto 0 auto;padding:24px 0;}.footer a{color:#363636;text-decoration:none;margin:0 8px;}@media only screen and (max-width:600px) {.header{padding:16px 4% 0 4%;}.header a:nth-of-type(3), .header a:nth-of-type(4){display:none;}form{margin:32px 4% 0 4%;}.text{margin:48px 4% 0 4%;}.footer{margin:64px 4% 0 4%;}}</style></head><body><div class=\"header\"><div><img src=\"/svg/1779005507/logo.svg\" width=\"180\" height=\"48\" alt=\"Y2Mate\"></div><div><a href=\"/\">Home</a><a href=\"/faq/\">FAQ</a><a href=\"/add-on/\">Add-On</a><a href=\"/bookmarklet/\">Bookmarklet</a></div></div><form autocomplete=\"off\" method=\"post\"><div class=\"form__title\"><label for=\"video\">Insert a YouTube video URL</label></div><div class=\"form__input\"><input id=\"video\" type=\"text\" name=\"video\" placeholder=\"youtube.com/watch?v=Y2MaTeR0cKs\" required autofocus></div><div class=\"form__actions\"><div class=\"form__formats\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"active\">MP3</button><button type=\"button\">MP4</button></div><button type=\"submit\">Convert</button></div></form><div class=\"text\"><h1>YouTube to MP3 Converter</h1><p>Y2Mate allows you to easily download YouTube videos as MP3 or MP4 files. The service is completely free and does not require any sign-up or additional software. Y2Mate is optimized to work seamlessly on all modern devices, including computers, mobile phones, and tablets.</p><p>Furthermore, the Y2Mate YouTube to MP3 Converter is not based on any third-party software. All conversions are processed using our own self-developed technology. This results in faster conversions and safe, verified file downloads.</p><p>By using Y2Mate, you accept our <a href=\"/terms-of-use/\">Terms of Use</a>.</p><p>How to download a YouTube video?</p><ol><li>Go to YouTube and search for a video you would like to download. Copy the video URL from your browser’s address bar. Please note: A valid YouTube video URL should look like this: youtube.com/watch?v=videoId.</li><li>Paste the video URL into the converter above and choose your preferred download format. You can select either MP3 or MP4. Please note: Videos that are converted to MP3 files can have a maximum length of 4 hours and will have a quality of 192kbps. Videos converted to MP4 can have a maximum length of 30 minutes and will have a quality of 360p. Click the &ldquo;Convert&rdquo; button.</li><li>The conversion process will start. Depending on the length of the video, this may take several minutes. As soon as the conversion is successfully completed, you can download the converted file by clicking the &ldquo;Download&rdquo; button.</li></ol><p>Many thanks for using our YouTube to MP3 Converter.</p></div><div class=\"footer\"><a href=\"/contact/\">Contact</a><a href=\"/copyright-claims/\">Copyright Claims</a><a href=\"/privacy-policy/\">Privacy Policy</a><a href=\"/terms-of-use/\">ToU</a></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"Y2Mate\",\"alternateName\":[\"YouTube MP3\",\"YouTube to MP3\",\"YouTube to MP3 Converter\",\"YouTube Converter\",\"YouTube Downloader\",\"y2mate.nu\"],\"url\":\"https://v3.y2mate.nu/\"}</script><script data-geo=\"0\" data-key=\"Yk5oRFFtb0RwTnZlbjhFVA==\" src=\"/js/1779005507/y2mate.js\" defer></script></body></html>"
